g><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ehv1665702690624.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ehv1665702690624.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ehv1665702690624.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ehv1665702690624\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $rettype\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ehv1665702690624___rettype_285610\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the retrieval mode of the outermost entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__topic_d88520e1_d88521e1_d88522e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__p_d88523e1_d88524e1_d88525e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__topic_d58942e1_d58943e1_d58944e1_d58945e1_d58946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712090e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__1\">\n Trigger\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n                              create\n                             </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 65\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Add occurrence\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 73\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Insert occurrence\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"6\">\n Read\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 43\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Retrieve additional occurrences (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span>)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 58\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Retrieve one additional occurrence (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/x</span>)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 78\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Next occurrence\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 82\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Retrieve\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 84\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Reconnect (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/reconnect</span>)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__2\">\n 110\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9527e1_d9528e1_d9529e1__entry__3\">\n Retrieve sequential\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1304\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ehv1665702690624__table_d9530e1_d9531e1_d9532e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function not allowed, unknown context. For example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span> was encountered outside the create and read triggers.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__topic_d58947e1_d58948e1_d58949e1_d58950e1_d58951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712090e273\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__topic_d58952e1_d58953e1_d58954e1_d58955e1_d58956e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712090e282\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__p_d88538e1_d88539e1_d88540e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span> returns the retrieval mode of the outermost entity. It should be used only in the read trigger or the create trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__p_d88541e1_d88542e1_d88543e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype</span> is set by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span> ProcScript statement and the ^ADD_OCC and ^INS_OCC structure editor functions.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__topic_d58957e1_d58958e1_d58959e1_d58960e1_d58961e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712090e304\">Example: Conditional Processing for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ehv1665702690624__p_d88547e1_d88548e1_d88549e1\">For example, query parameters are only used on the first <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span> statement to generate the database select instruction. On consequent reads these parameters are ignored. so you can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rettype==78</span> ( Next occurrence) to prevent unnecessary code execution for potential query parameter processing.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger read\n if ($rettype != 78)\n ; Construct query and order information here\n read u_where (something…) order by ….\n else\n ; No need to construct any query and order info, because it is ignored for subsequent occurrences\n read\n endif\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qzx1665702660750.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger create</a><p>Trigger that handles a user’s request to add or insert a new occurrence of the entity in a Form.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/grx1665703129707.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger read</a><p>System trigger that fetches an occurrence from the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$rettype Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $rettype Return the retrieval mode of the outermost entity. $rettype Return Values Table 1. Values returned by $rettype Trigger Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. create 65 Add occurrence 73 Insert occurrence Read 43 Retrieve additional occurrences ( retrieve/a ) 58 Retrieve one additional occurrence ( retrieve/x ) 78 Next occurrence 82 Retrieve 84 Reconnect ( retrieve/reconnect ) 110 Retrieve sequential Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $rettype Value Error constant Meaning -1304 <UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT> Function not allowed, unknown context. For example, $rettype was encountered outside the create and read triggers. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $rettype returns the retrieval mode of the outermost entity. It should be used only in the read trigger or the create trigger. $rettype is set by the read ProcScript statement and the ^ADD_OCC and ^INS_OCC structure editor functions. Example: Conditional Processing for read For example, query parameters are only used on the first read statement to generate the database select instruction. On consequent reads these parameters are ignored. so you can use $rettype==78 ( Next occurrence) to prevent unnecessary code execution for potential query parameter processing. trigger read if ($rettype != 78) ; Construct query and order information here read u_where (something…) order by …. else ; No need to construct any query and order info, because it is ignored for subsequent occurrences read endif end Copy Related Links trigger create Trigger that handles a user’s request to add or insert a new occurrence of the entity in a Form. trigger read System trigger that fetches an occurrence from the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}